transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Hello. Hello. Hello. Haan, haan Himanshu ji, Anurag baat kar raha tha IndiaMART se.
Executive: Haan ji, haan ji.
Customer: Haan aapka call aaya tha sir dusre wale number se.
Executive: Call aaya tha?
Customer: Ji, ji, ji woh jo primary number hai na aapka 462 wala, woh aap hi ka hai na abhi?
Executive: Haan, lekin.
Customer: Kaun, kab aaya tha?
Executive: Just abhi aaya hai, thodi der pehle customer care pe call aayi hai aapki.
Customer: Nahi, nahi, maine call nahi kiya tha.
Customer: Aap hi ki usse call dial hui sir, mere paas toh ticket bhi raise ho gayi hai.
Executive: Sorry, sorry, maine call nahi kiya tha. Mera number toh office mein hai.
Customer: Haan, toh yeh number use hua bhi nahi hai?
Customer: Nahi, 5:15 pe call aayi hai, toh kahi ticket open hui hai.
Executive: Abhi, abhi, abhi just, abhi dekhte hai. Dekh ke bata rahe hai aapko.
Customer: Haan sir, mujhe jaldi se bata dijiye, nahi puchhenge kya dikkat hai.
Customer: Hai na?
Executive: Main batata hu. Haan.
